
---

**StreamDeltaFrame**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes numeric stream changes as deltas within a frame window, highlighting acceleration and volatility.

```markdown
# StreamDeltaFrame - Realtime Stream Change Visualizer

StreamDeltaFrame renders moving data as relative deltas within a fixed frame to expose sharp shifts and instabilities.

## Features
- Frame-based delta chart  
- Custom smoothing / decay  
- Matplotlib visualization

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/StreamDeltaFrame.git
cd StreamDeltaFrame
python visualize.py
